questions.question: For at least 10 frames, a rubber object o0 is behind another object o1, and an object o2 is on the left side of the video frame. For the following duration of at least 15 frames, o0 is far from o2, o1 is to the left of o0, and o2 is also to the left of o0. Finally, for another duration of at least 15 frames, o2 is shaped like a sphere.
questions.dsl: Duration((Behind(o0, o1), Left(o2), Material(o0, 'rubber')), 10); Duration((Far(o0, o2, 3.0), LeftOf(o1, o0), LeftOf(o2, o0)), 15); Duration(Shape(o2, 'sphere'), 15)

questions.question: A red object o0 on the right side of the frame is to the left of another object o1 for at least 10 frames. Then, o1 is in front of o0 and to the right of o0 for at least 5 frames. Finally, there's a rubber object o2 on the left side of the frame.
questions.dsl: Duration((Color(o0, 'red'), LeftOf(o0, o1), Right(o0)), 10); Duration((FrontOf(o1, o0), RightOf(o1, o0)), 5); (Left(o2), Material(o2, 'rubber'))

questions.question: A blue object o0 is present while another object o1 is on the left side of the frame, and object o2 is to the right of o1. Then, for at least 10 frames, the blue object o0 is made of rubber, and both o1 and o2 are at the top of the frame while being close to each other.
questions.dsl: (Color(o0, 'blue'), Left(o1), RightOf(o2, o1)); Duration((Material(o0, 'rubber'), Near(o1, o2, 1.0), Top(o1), Top(o2)), 10)

questions.question: There is a metal object o0, while object o1 is to the right of o2. Following that, o2 is to the left of o0 and near o1 while also being at the top of the frame for at least 10 frames. Then, for another duration of at least 10 frames, o2 is in front of o0, o1 is also in front of o0, and o0 has a cube shape.
questions.dsl: (Material(o0, 'metal'), RightOf(o1, o2)); Duration((LeftOf(o2, o0), Near(o2, o1, 1.0), Top(o2)), 10); Duration((FrontOf(o2, o0), FrontOf(o1, o0), Shape(o0, 'cube')), 10)

questions.question: A spherical object o0 is located at the bottom of the video frame for at least 10 frames. Then, a rubber object o1 is on the left side of the frame. In the following sequence, which lasts for at least 15 frames, o1 is behind o0, o0 is in front of another object o2, and o0 is on the left side of the frame.
questions.dsl: Duration((Bottom(o0), Shape(o0, 'sphere')), 10); (Left(o1), Material(o1, 'rubber')); Duration((Behind(o1, o0), FrontOf(o0, o2), Left(o0)), 15)

questions.question: For at least 5 frames, an object o0 is behind another object o1 and in front of a third object o2. Then o0 is at the bottom of the video frame and in front of o1. Finally, for a duration of at least 15 frames, o0 is on the left side of the frame and made of rubber.
questions.dsl: Duration((Behind(o0, o1), FrontOf(o0, o2)), 5); (Bottom(o0), FrontOf(o0, o1)); Duration((Left(o0), Material(o0, 'rubber'), Material(o0, 'rubber')), 15)

questions.question: Initially, an object o0 is at the top of the video frame for at least 10 frames. Then, for at least 5 frames, there is an object o1 at the bottom of the frame, while o0 is cyan and to the left of o1, and o1 is on the right side of the frame and in front of o0. Finally, for another duration of at least 5 frames, o1 is to the left of another rubber object o2.
questions.dsl: Duration(Top(o0), 10); Duration((Bottom(o1), Color(o0, 'cyan'), FrontOf(o1, o0), LeftOf(o0, o1), Right(o1)), 5); Duration((LeftOf(o1, o2), Material(o2, 'rubber')), 5)

questions.question: For at least 5 frames, an object o0 is far from another object o1, and simultaneously, an object o2 is on the left side of the video frame. Subsequently, o2 is made of rubber and o1 is shaped like a cube. Finally, for at least 15 frames, o2 is behind o0, o1 is in front of o0, and moreover, o0 is to the left of o1.
questions.dsl: Duration((Far(o0, o1, 3.0), Left(o2)), 5); (Material(o2, 'rubber'), Shape(o1, 'cube')); Duration((Behind(o2, o0), FrontOf(o1, o0), LeftOf(o0, o1)), 15)

questions.question: For at least 10 frames, an object o0 is behind another object o1. Then, for a duration of at least 5 frames, o1 is in front of o0, an object o2 is on the left side of the video frame, o0 is shaped like a cylinder, and o1 is shaped like a sphere. Finally, for at least 15 frames, o2 is to the left of both o0 and o1, while o1 is on the right side of the video frame.
questions.dsl: Duration(Behind(o0, o1), 10); Duration((FrontOf(o1, o0), Left(o2), Shape(o0, 'cylinder'), Shape(o1, 'sphere')), 5); Duration((LeftOf(o2, o0), LeftOf(o2, o1), Right(o1)), 15)

questions.question: For at least 15 frames, an object o0 is in front of another object o1, and o1 is to the right of a third object o2. Following this, for a duration of at least 10 frames, both o0 and o2 are to the left of o1, which is made of rubber, o2 is near o1, and o0 is shaped like a sphere.
questions.dsl: Duration((FrontOf(o0, o1), RightOf(o1, o2)), 15); Duration((LeftOf(o2, o1), LeftOf(o0, o1), Material(o1, 'rubber'), Near(o2, o1, 1.0), Shape(o0, 'sphere')), 10)
